narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is a great class for a political science student that doesn't mind a bit of reading. Class discussions are always very engaging.

I absolutely would recommend the course. This course brings history and insight to American political thinking. The diversity of thought between and among the students and professor is intriguing and relevant.
Yes, I would highly recommend it, especially as a first seminar to take.
